    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In addition to <code>Optimize Imports</code> and <code>Auto Import</code>, which were pointed out by @dave-newton and @ryan-stewart in earlier answers, go to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>IDEA &lt;= 13: <code>File menu &gt; Settings &gt; Code Style &gt; Java &gt; Imports</code></li>\n<li>IDEA >= 14: <code>File menu &gt; Settings &gt; Editor &gt; Code Style &gt; Java &gt; Imports</code> (thanks to @mathias-bader for the hint!)\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/lWLqY.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/lWLqY.png\" alt=\"Settings dialog\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>There you can fine tune the grouping and order or imports, \"<code>Class count to use import with '*'</code>\", etc.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Note:</strong><br/>\nsince IDEA 13 you can configure the project default settings from the IDEA \"start page\": <code>Configure &gt; Project defaults &gt; Settings &gt; ...</code>. Then every new project will have those default settings:\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/y8hjV.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/y8hjV.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></a></p>\n"
  }, {
