      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "You are right, it is not a thoughtful judgment in normal situations. It is - however - a vented frustration on a stunningly missing basic feature from an ultimate tool. I spent 2 hours in agony trying to get this simple, essential feature to work, without success. And what made it worse, rather than been a built in feature by default (like how elegantly Eclipse does it) a plugin really needed to be written to achieve that! Its like building the a state of the art and most complex jumbo jet but without  air-conditioning, instead, each passenger is given a paper fan! It took me 1 sec in Eclipse."
