    "body" : "<p>That plugin will automatically do the \"organize import\" action on file save: <a href=\"https://github.com/dubreuia/intellij-plugin-save-actions\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/dubreuia/intellij-plugin-save-actions</a>.</p>\n\n<p>To install: \"File > Settings > Plugins > Browse repositories... > Search 'Save Actions' > Category 'Code tools'\". Then activate the \"organize import\" save action.</p>\n"
