      "body" : "I had the sam frustration, however, @Ryan is correct.  <code>CTRL ALT O</code>  , can add the missing imports. But you have to configure it in Setting &gt; Editor -&gt; General &gt; Auto Import, and check &quot;Add unambigous imports on the fly&quot; Then resolves all imports in a class."
