    "answer_id" : 31440282,
    "question_id" : 8608710,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>July 2015 - I have concluded that IntelliJ does not support automatically resolving imports with a single function. \"Organize imports\" simply removes unused imports, it does not resolve unimported types. Control-Space resolves a single unimported type. There does not exist a single action to resolve all types' imports.</p>\n"
