    "answer_id" : 75446284,
    "question_id" : 8608710,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I did not have any wildcard * as mentioned in one of the answers, neither did any of the formatting through Android Studio mentioned worked</p>\n<p>What helped was running this:</p>\n<pre><code>./gradlew ktlintFormat\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 4528798,
      "reputation" : 11833,
      "user_id" : 3679900,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 48,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/tFAHl.png?s=256",
      "display_name" : "y2k-shubham",
